{"tid":714742,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解班港女結婚/大肚要貼相上fb","createTime":"2018-06-24T00:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T07:21:06.000Z","uid":151774,"like":12,"dislike":106,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b563552c4fdf9835d7f41d0fba4d0b5e6270ea5a","tid":714742,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T00:07:36.000Z","msg":"曬命 ？好自豪？好開心？<br />\n有乜好自豪？有乜咁開心？<br />\n有d 仲攬住老豆老母喊 好嘔心<br />\n養大個女廿幾年最後送俾人抽插<br />\n咁有咩值得高興? 係 結婚屌閪好正常<br />\n但點解要公諸於世 ？見好多幾年之後離婚<br />\n之前貼啲結婚相刪都刪唔切 無用了<br />\n全世界都知你係二手閪 唔值錢<br />\n無留後路俾自己 懶係好開心咁<br />\n著下旗袍化個馬嬲屎忽就以為自己係李嘉欣<br />\n屌 原來嫁個公屋仔 笑撚死我"},{"pid":"10807c98a1fc1f53ae916b8e96294df96c188b3a","tid":714742,"uid":151774,"like":3,"dislike":32,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T00:16:38.000Z","msg":"你又唔係明星 又唔係嫁高富帥<br />\n嫁個公屋仔都up萬9 幾張相話俾人知你個閪俾人屌到臭9哂<br />\n話俾全世界知你老豆老母辛苦廿年養大你<br />\n但你又閪痕 俾人中出 臭9哂迫住嫁<br />\n真丢架 每次睇到fb ig.有臭閪貼結婚相<br />\n我一樣會睇哂去  一路睇一路恥笑<br />\n個嘴一路口upup 臭閪臭閪臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ed007a4dcb8ebd485c501420533db7541dcbab","tid":714742,"uid":151774,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T00:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/081728_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F081728_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c09c57a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ef008b1407df6e667cb305fc8b345bef26a9920","tid":714742,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T00:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/081759_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F081759_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=71f9427e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1bb54854c6ac1afb8dc8999dd6b9a1305f724fb","tid":714742,